  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Whether a mapping algorithm &quot;Ripple-mapping&quot; is able to rapidly identify the areas of
      long-duration multicomponent electrograms which constitute the targets for ablation for an
      automated strategy remains to be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
